  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink53-kilavi">talaivi taṉṉuṭaṉ pōyp puṉalāṭiyavaḻi, ‘itu parattaiyaruṭaṉāṭiya
          tuṟai’ eṉa niṉaintu piṟanta melivai
          maraittamaiyai
          yuṇarnta talaimakaṉ maṉaivayiṟ pukuntuḻi, ‘teyvaṅkaḷ uṟaiyum tuṟaikkaṇṇē nām āṭiṉavataṉāl
          piṟantatukol niṉakku ivvēṟupāṭu’ eṉṟu viṉāyiṉāṟku avaḷ colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink53">
          <l>tuṟaiyeva ṉaṇaṅkum yāmuṟṟa nōyē</l>
          <l>ciṟaiyaḻi putuppuṉal pāynteṉak kalaṅkik</l>
          <l>kaḻaṉit tāmarai malarum</l>
          <l>paḻaṉa vūranī yuṟṟa cūḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg xml:lang="en">


<l>           O man from the village of paddy fields! </l> 
<l rend="indent2">           Where lotuses blooming in tanks</l> 
<l rend="indent2">           are stirred up because of the fresh flood</l> 
<l rend="indent2">           gushing in after bursting its banks – </l> 
<l>         What will haunt the ghat? The pain we have suffered</l> 
<l>         or the [broken] promises you have made us suffer?  </l> 
        

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
